title: Zelenskyy says Trump exerting undue pressure on Kyiv as Ukraine-Russia peace talks enter second day – Europe live
summary_full: US-brokered negotiations in Switzerland began on Tuesday but expectations for breakthroughs are lowWhile peace talks are taking place, the Ukrainian energy ministry reported that four regions are without power this morning due to Russian attacks against infrastructure.Thousands are affected by the power outages in Odesa, Zaporizhzhia and Dnipropetrovsk in the south and Sumy in the north-east, the ministry said in a Telegram post.
